sdp/verification/t-001@20260416t181925zb-verify.md:14:The implementation of `diff_scores` correctly identifies note-level changes (scale degree, duration, accent), phrase-level changes (dynamics, voice, role, metadata), and global changes (tempo, key). The `ScoreDelta.summary()` method provides a clear, human-readable summary of these changes. All 16 unit tests for the diff utility pass, covering various scenarios including added/removed notes and phrases, and identical scores.
sdp/verification/t-001@20260416t181925zb-verify.md:17:The structured delta (`ScoreDelta`, `NoteDelta`, `PhraseDelta`) captures all requested aspects of the score changes (changed notes, dynamics, articulations via `accent`, timing via `duration_beats` and `tempo_delta`). The utility provides the necessary summary functionality as requested.
